"{\"uid\": \"english.aawsat.com-sports-5046976-katie-ledecky-swims-history-800-freestyle-victory-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Every year on Aug. 3, Katie Ledecky is reminded of her first Olympic gold medal.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 80, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 22, \"end\": 35, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Ledecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was just 15 years old, a reserved high schooler who had surprisingly made the US swim team for the London Games.\", \"from\": 82, \"to\": 198, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 164, \"end\": 166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999831279639, \"rank\": 1.687212141320509e-08, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then she went out and shocked the world, beating everyone in the 800-meter freestyle.\", \"from\": 199, \"to\": 284, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Twelve years to the day, Ledecky did it again.\", \"from\": 286, \"to\": 332, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Not a stunner, but one for the ages.\", \"from\": 334, \"to\": 370, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gold medal No.\", \"from\": 372, \"to\": 386, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"9.\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 389, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ledecky capped another stellar Olympics by becoming only the second swimmer to win an event at four straight Summer Games, holding off Ariarne Titmus, the \\\"Terminator,\\\" to win the 800 free Saturday night.\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 595, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 52