she said.\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1150, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, when I saw it was Aug. 3, I was like, 'Oh boy, I have got to get the job done.'\\\"\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1236, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That she did, going faster than her winning time in Tokyo to finish in 8 minutes, 11.04 seconds.\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1334, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1290, \"end\": 1295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.875305294466866e-14, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Titmus was right on her shoulder nearly the entire race, but Ledecky pulled away in the final 100.\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1433, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1335, \"end\": 1341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Titmus, who beat Ledecky in the 400 freestyle, settled for silver at 8:12.29.\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1512, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1435, \"end\": 1441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The bronze went to another American, Paige Madden at 8:13.00.\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1574, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1540, \"end\": 1548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.8248020207093426, \"rank\": 0.21241216045199013, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"