e\": \"\\\"That's how remarkable she is.\\\"\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 2007, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Their friendly rivalry has driven both to greater heights.\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2067, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They each won two golds and four medals at these games, which pushed Ledecky to 14 overall and left the 23-year-old Aussie with four golds and eight medals in her career.\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2238, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To think that ...\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2258, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I challenged her into her fourth consecutive in the 800 is pretty cool,\\\" Titmus said.\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2332, \"end\": 2338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel very honored and privileged to be her rival, and I hope I have made her a better athlete.\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2442, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She has certainly made me become the athlete I am.\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2493, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt so privileged to race alongside her.\\\"\", \"from\": 2494, \"to\": 2538, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ledecky has dominated the distance freestyle events over the last dozen years - and is not done yet.\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2640, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She's made it clear she plans to keep swimming at least through the 2028 Los Angeles Games.\", \"from\": 2641, \"to\": 2732, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not easy,\\\" Ledecky said.\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2764, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will take it year by year, and we will see if I can keep giving everything I have got for as long as I have 