\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Britain was seventh this time.\", \"from\": 5486, \"to\": 5516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5486, \"end\": 5493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9999722017135616, \"rank\": 2.7799059233864696e-05, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The US bumped its total to six golds, one behind leading Australia with four events remaining Sunday.\", \"from\": 5518, \"to\": 5619, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5522, \"end\": 5524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999831279639, \"rank\": 1.687212141320509e-08, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 5575, \"end\": 5584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9833140120854065, \"rank\": 0.009267319907680871, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Americans are assured of winning the overall medal count with 25.\", \"from\": 5620, \"to\": 5689, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5620, \"end\": 5633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.786004254999228e-44, \"text\": \"The Americans\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hungarian claims butterfly gold  Krist\\u00f3f Mil\\u00e