, \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mil\\u00e1k had failed to defend his Olympic title in the 200 butterfly, settling for a silver behind Marchand.\", \"from\": 6001, \"to\": 6106, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6097, \"end\": 6105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.27008346879594e-17, \"text\": \"Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mil\\u00e1k claimed silver in the 100 fly three years ago, but he did not have to worry about the guy who beat him in that race.\", \"from\": 6108, \"to\": 6230, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"American Caeleb Dressel stunningly failed to qualify for the final.\", \"from\": 6231, \"to\": 6298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6231, \"end\": 6239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.8248020207093426, \"rank\": 0.21241216045199013, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 6240, \"end\": 6254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caeleb Dressel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kharun added another bronze to the one he garnered in the 200 butterfly.\", \"from\": 6300, \"to\": 6372, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Isack Hadjar will replace Yuki Tsunoda in the hot seat as Max Verstappen's Red Bull teammate next season with Arvid Lindblad joining Liam Lawson at Racing Bulls, the Formula One teams announced on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 6374, \"to\": 6579, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6374, \"end\": 6386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isack_Hadjar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Isack Hadjar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isack_Hadjar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isack_Hadjar\"}, {\"begin\": 6400, \"end\": 6412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yuki_Tsunoda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yuki Tsunoda\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yuki_Tsunoda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yuki_Tsunoda\"}, {\"begin\": 6432, \"end\": 6446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Verstappen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Max Verstappen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Verstappen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Verstappen\"}, {\"begin\": 6490, \"end\": 6498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Diablo_Silverado_Council\", \"score\": 0.6374393458473545, \"rank\": 0.5687766727292427, \"text\": \"Lindblad\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Diablo_Silverado_Council\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Diablo_Silverado_Council\"}, {\"begin\": 6507, \"end\": 6518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liam_Lawson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Liam Lawson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liam_Lawson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liam_Lawson\"}, {\"begin\": 6540, \"end\": 6551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Formula_One\", \"score\": 0.9999999520032372, \"rank\": 4.7996889360970334e-08, \"text\": \"Formula One\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Formula_One\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Formula_One\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Frenchman Hadjar, 21, has made a big impression in his debut season with sister team Racing Bulls including taking his first podium with third place in the Dutch Grand Prix at the end of August.\", \"from\": 6581, \"to\": 6775, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"British-born Lindblad, who also has Swedish nationality and Indian heritage through his mother, moves up from Formula Two to partner New Zealander Lawson and will be the sole rookie on the 2026 grid.\", \"from\": 6777, \"to\": 6976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6790, \"end\": 6798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Diablo_Silverado_Council\", \"score\": 0.6374393458473545, \"rank\": 0.5687766727292427, \"text\": \"Lindblad\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Diablo_Silverado_Council\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Diablo_Silverado_Council\"}, {\"begin\": 6813, \"end\": 6820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"score\": 0.9999999999354259, \"rank\": 6.440074867197176e-11, \"text\": \"Swedish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\"}, {\"begin\": 6837, \"end\": 6843, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3240531298004636e-13, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 6887, \"end\": 6898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIA_Formula_2_Championship\", \"score\": 0.9999108169929992, \"rank\": 8.919096119849062e-05, \"text\": \"Formula Two\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIA_Formula_2_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIA_Formula_2_Championship\"}, {\"begin\": 6924, \"end\": 6930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Lawson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.054804748444635e-17, \"text\": \"Lawson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Lawson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Lawson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tsunoda's departure leaves Formula One without a Japanese driver on the starting grid.\", \"from\": 6978, \"to\": 7064, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7005, \"end\": 7016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Formula_One\", \"score\": 0.9999999520032372, \"rank\": 4.7996889360970334e-08, \"text\": \"Formula One\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Formula_One\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Formula_One\"}, {\"begin\": 7027, \"end\": 7035, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9991879579030449, \"rank\": 0.0005592247017337442, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Red Bull said he will remain within the \\\"family\\\" as test and reserve driver for the first season of a new engine era.\", \"from\": 7065, \"to\": 7182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tsunoda will also serve as Racing Bulls reserve when compatriot Ayu Iwasa, this year's Japanese Super Formula champion, is not available.\", \"from\": 7184, \"to\": 7321, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7248, \"end\": 7251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayumi_Hamasaki\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.033777628460257e-31, \"text\": \"Ayu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayumi_Hamasaki\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayumi_Hamasaki\"}, {\"begin\": 7271, \"end\": 7279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9991879579030449, \"rank\": 0.0005592247017337442, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 7280, \"end\": 7293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Formula_Championship\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.22799758235355e-27, \"text\": \"Super Formula\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Formula_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Formula_Championship\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We believe Isack can thrive alongside Max and produce the magic on track,\\\" said Red Bull principal Laurent Mekies.\", \"from\": 7323, \"to\": 7438, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7362, \"end\": 7365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Branning\", \"score\": 0.9999999987367119, \"rank\": 1.2625689762998424e-09, \"text\": \"Max\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Branning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Branning\"}, {\"begin\": 7423, \"end\": 7437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurent_Mekies\", \"score\": 0.9999983868641998, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laurent Mekies\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurent_Mekies\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurent_Mekies\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HOTTEST SEAT IN FORMULA ONE  The role of teammate to four-times world champion Verstappen, who could yet add a fifth title in a row at Sunday's season-ending Abu Dhabi Grand Prix, has been something of a poisoned chalice for a string of hopefuls.\", \"from\": 7440, \"to\": 7686, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7598, \"end\": 7618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2021_Abu_Dhabi_Grand_Prix\", \"score\": 0.9999999976571416, \"rank\": 2.0386510927263396e-09, \"text\": \"Abu Dhabi Grand Prix\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2021_Abu_Dhabi_Grand_Prix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2021_Abu_Dhabi_Grand_Prix\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Verstappen, the absolute number one driver, will start 2026 with his fourth different teammate since the last race of 2024.\", \"from\": 7688, \"to\": 7811, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No teammate has come close to the Dutch driver's relentless form since Mexican Sergio Perez took four podiums in the first five races last season and then suffered a dramatic loss of pace before departing.\", \"from\": 7813, \"to\": 8018, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7847, \"end\": 7852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9996860396380591, \"rank\": 0.0003140589591813647, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 7884, \"end\": 7891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9999997857203428, \"rank\": 2.0058322245831614e-07, \"text\": \"Mexican\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\"}, {\"begin\": 7892, \"end\": 7904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sergio_P\\u00e9rez\", \"score\": 0.9999999868259694, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sergio Perez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sergio_P\\u00e9rez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sergio_P\\u00e9rez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before him Alex Albon, now at Williams, and Pierre Gasly, who moved to Renault-owned Alpine, also struggled to keep up.\", \"from\": 8020, \"to\": 8139, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8031, \"end\": 8041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Albon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alex Albon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Albon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Albon\"}, {\"begin\": 8064, \"end\": 8076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_Gasly\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pierre Gasly\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_Gasly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_Gasly\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lawson started this season as the incumbent but was replaced by Tsunoda after two races without scoring.\", \"from\": 8141, \"to\": 8245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8141, \"end\": 8147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Lawson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.054804748444635e-17, \"text\": \"Lawson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Lawson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Lawson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Japanese has been completely eclipsed by Verstappen, with the champion winning seven races and scoring 396 points while Tsunoda's tally stands at a mere 33.\", \"from\": 8247, \"to\": 8407, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8251, \"end\": 8259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9991879579030449, \"rank\": 0.0005592247017337442, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After all the hard work I have put in since joining the junior team, it's such a great reward,\\\" said Hadjar.\", \"from\": 8409, \"to\": 8518, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have had many ups and downs throughout my career, and they kept believing and pushing me.\", \"from\": 8519, \"to\": 8611, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel ready to go... and I am happy and proud they feel the same.\", \"from\": 8613, \"to\": 8680, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's an awesome move, to work with the best and learn from Max is something I can not wait for.\\\"\", \"from\": 8681, \"to\": 8777, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8740, \"end\": 8743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Branning\", \"score\": 0.9999999987367119, \"rank\": 1.2625689762998424e-09, \"text\": \"Max\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Branning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Branning\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lindblad will take his place as the 20th Red Bull junior driver to reach Formula One and he recognized the challenge ahead.\", \"from\": 8779, \"to\": 8902, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8779, \"end\": 8787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Diablo_Silverado_Council\", \"score\": 0.6374393458473545, \"rank\": 0.5687766727292427, \"text\": \"Lindblad\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Diablo_Silverado_Council\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Diablo_Silverado_Council\"}, {\"begin\": 8820, \"end\": 8835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Bull_Junior_Team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Red Bull junior\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Bull_Junior_Team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Bull_Junior_Team\"}, {\"begin\": 8852, \"end\": 8863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Formula_One\", \"score\": 0.9999999520032372, \"rank\": 4.7996889360970334e-08, \"text\": \"Formula One\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Formula_One\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Formula_One\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know there is a lot to learn, but I am ready to work closely with the team and rise to it.\", \"from\": 8904, \"to\": 8997, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not wait to get started, it's going to be an exciting year,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 8998, \"to\": 9073, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Team boss Alan Permane said Lawson, 23, and Lindblad, 18, would be a strong and dynamic pairing.\", \"from\": 9075, \"to\": 9171, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9085, \"end\": 9097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Permane\", \"score\": 0.9999698415031455, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alan Permane\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Permane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Permane\"}, {\"begin\": 9103, \"end\": 9109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Lawson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.054804748444635e-17, \"text\": \"Lawson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Lawson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Lawson\"}, {\"begin\": 9119, \"end\": 9127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Diablo_Silverado_Council\", \"score\": 0.6374393458473545, \"rank\": 0.5687766727292427, \"text\": \"Lindblad\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Diablo_Silverado_Council\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Diablo_Silverado_Council\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He (Lawson) has excelled when conditions have been at their hardest and we look forward to building on this in 2026, while Arvid's rapid progression marks him as one of the standout young talents in the sport,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 9173, \"to\": 9393, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9178, \"end\": 9184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Lawson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.054804748444635e-17, \"text\": \"Lawson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Lawson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Lawson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Arne Slot admitted on Tuesday that \\\"superhuman\\\" Mohamed Salah was unhappy about being omitted from Liverpool's team for their vital 2-0 win against West Ham, but praised his attitude.\", \"from\": 9395, \"to\": 9578, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9443, \"end\": 9456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Salah\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7006330011399334e-80, \"text\": \"Mohamed Salah\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Salah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Salah\"}, {\"begin\": 9494, \"end\": 9503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.626019739739782e-33, \"text\": \"Liverpool\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 9548, \"end\": 9551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ham\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.2426216411518586e-19, \"text\": \"Ham\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ham\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Egypt forward was an unused substitute at the London Stadium on Sunday as Liverpool boss Slot made changes following a terrible run of nine defeats in 12 games in all competitions, said AFP.\", \"from\": 9580, \"to\": 9774, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9584, \"end\": 9589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.2850321252195793e-12, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 9658, \"end\": 9667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.626019739739782e-33, \"text\": \"Liverpool\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 9770, \"end\": 9773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.057285370053546e-14, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Misfiring Salah, 33, has scored just four Premier League goals this season -- in stark contrast to his haul of 29 last season, a tally that won him the Golden Boot.\", \"from\": 9776, \"to\": 9940, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9786, \"end\": 9791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Salah\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.147486801863164e-27, \"text\": \"Salah\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Salah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Salah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Slot told reporters that during his reign as manager at Anfield, Salah had been a \\\"superhuman being\\\" but that he had not been at his best in recent weeks.\", \"from\": 9942, \"to\": 10096, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9998, \"end\": 10005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anfield\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1169162408571518e-85, \"text\": \"Anfield\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anfield\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anfield\"}, {\"begin\": 10007, \"end\": 10012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Salah\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.147486801863164e-27, \"text\": \"Salah\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Salah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Salah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As with all players around the world, there are also phases in your time at the club that you are human,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 10098, \"to\": 10213, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But he's scored so many goals for us and I am sure he will in the future.\\\"\", \"from\": 10214, \"to\": 10289, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Slot, whose eighth-placed team host high-flying Sunderland on Wednesday, said he was not surprised by Salah's reaction to being left out, praising his professionalism.\", \"from\": 10291, \"to\": 10458, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10339, \"end\": 10349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunderland_A.F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.770068365250748e-31, \"text\": \"Sunderland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunderland_A.F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunderland_A.F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 10393, \"end\": 10398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Salah\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.147486801863164e-27, \"text\": \"Salah\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Salah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Salah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's a normal reaction from a player that's good enough to play for us,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 10460, \"to\": 10544, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I say it mildly, because he's been so outstanding for this club for so many years, and will be for us in the future.\", \"from\": 10545, \"to\": 10666, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, yeah, of course a player is not happy when they are not playing.\", \"from\": 10668, \"to\": 10737, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He wasn't the only one who wasn't happy that he wasn't starting, I can tell you.\\\"\", \"from\": 10738, \"to\": 10819, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Dutchman said that Salah had been supportive of his teammates.\", \"from\": 10821, \"to\": 10887, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10821, \"end\": 10833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Dutchman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Dutchman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Dutchman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Dutchman\"}, {\"begin\": 10844, \"end\": 10849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Salah\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.147486801863164e-27, \"text\": \"Salah\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Salah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Salah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You cannot be a player that's available every three days and play on that high standard if you go with your emotions,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 10889, \"to\": 11017, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But Mo is so disciplined, knows what to do to stay fit, and no matter if he plays well, does not play well, if he plays or if he does not play, he will always be that top professional.\\\"\", \"from\": 11019, \"to\": 11205, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11024, \"end\": 11026, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mo_Harris\", \"score\": 0.7880592298821628, \"rank\": 0.2689044937805317, \"text\": \"Mo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mo_Harris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mo_Harris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Slot said that Salah was scheduled to leave for the Africa Cup of Nations on December 15.\", \"from\": 11207, \"to\": 11296, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11222, \"end\": 11227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Salah\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.147486801863164e-27, \"text\": \"Salah\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Salah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Salah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As always in these situations, there is a player involved, there is the nation involved -- Egypt in this situation -- and the club.\", \"from\": 11298, \"to\": 11430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11390, \"end\": 11395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.2850321252195793e-12, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And there are always talks about what is best for all three of us,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 11431, \"to\": 11507, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When the 2025 season revved into gear in Melbourne back in March, there was every expectation that this would be a championship to savor.\", \"from\": 11509, \"to\": 11646, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11550, \"end\": 11559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"score\": 0.9976062131814062, \"rank\": 0.0023995307147868846, \"text\": \"Melbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even though Max Verstappen had collected a fourth successive title in 2024, the pace of the McLarens of Lando Norris and Oscar Piastri in the second half of the season suggested that this year would be tight.\", \"from\": 11648, \"to\": 11856, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11660, \"end\": 11674, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Verstappen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Max Verstappen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Verstappen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Verstappen\"}, {\"begin\": 11752, \"end\": 11764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lando_Norris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lando Norris\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lando_Norris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lando_Norris\"}, {\"begin\": 11769, \"end\": 11782, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Piastri\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Oscar Piastri\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Piastri\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Piastri\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And so, it has proved with the three of them still slugging away for the title as the 24-race season comes to a conclusion in Abu Dhabi on Sunday, with Norris 12 points ahead of Verstappen and Piastri a further four points back.\", \"from\": 11858, \"to\": 12086, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11984, \"end\": 11993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yas_Marina_Circuit\", \"score\": 0.9999999994743121, \"rank\": 5.259280919523802e-10, \"text\": \"Abu Dhabi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yas_Marina_Circuit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yas_Marina_Circuit\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"AFP looks back at some of the key moments that built up to such a gripping climax:  China service  If the season started well for McLaren with victory for Norris in Melbourne, it was near perfect in the second race in Shanghai as Piastri led home a 1-2 that sent a warning through the pitlane.\", \"from\": 12088, \"to\": 12381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12218, \"end\": 12225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McLaren\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.387695858836223e-53, \"text\": \"McLaren\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McLaren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McLaren\"}, {\"begin\": 12243, \"end\": 12249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lando_Norris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.976005406009526e-69, \"text\": \"Norris\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lando_Norris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lando_Norris\"}, {\"begin\": 12253, \"end\": 12262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"score\": 0.9976062131814062, \"rank\": 0.0023995307147868846, \"text\": \"Melbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\"}, {\"begin\": 12306, \"end\": 12314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai_International_Circuit\", \"score\": 0.9991472343190009, \"rank\": 0.0008534935106225845, \"text\": \"Shanghai\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai_International_Circuit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai_International_Circuit\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The McLarens were undoubtedly the best cars on the grid -- it would take something special to stop them.\", \"from\": 12383, \"to\": 12487, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Verstappen finished fourth for Red Bull, but the team announced later that his teammate Liam Lawson was being demoted with immediate effect to their sister Racing Bulls team, to be replaced by Yuki Tsunoda.\", \"from\": 12489, \"to\": 12695, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12577, \"end\": 12588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liam_Lawson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Liam Lawson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liam_Lawson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liam_Lawson\"}, {\"begin\": 12682, \"end\": 12694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yuki_Tsunoda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yuki Tsunoda\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yuki_Tsunoda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yuki_Tsunoda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Miami vice  Piastri began to emerge as the dominant McLaren driver and their likely world champion as he picked up three wins on the bounce: in Bahrain, Saudi Arabia and Miami to make it four wins from the first six races.\", \"from\": 12697, \"to\": 12919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12697, \"end\": 12707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami_Vice\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.776483761379625e-57, \"text\": \"Miami vice\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami_Vice\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami_Vice\"}, {\"begin\": 12749, \"end\": 12756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McLaren\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.387695858836223e-53, \"text\": \"McLaren\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McLaren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McLaren\"}, {\"begin\": 12841, \"end\": 12848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bahrain_International_Circuit\", \"score\": 0.9999999997535269, \"rank\": 2.467720828654667e-10, \"text\": \"Bahrain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bahrain_International_Circuit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bahrain_International_Circuit\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That win in Miami extended his lead over Norris to 16 points.\", \"from\": 12921, \"to\": 12982, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12933, \"end\": 12938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami_Hurricanes_football\", \"score\": 0.9999786963940157, \"rank\": 1.3142795691288688e-05, \"text\": \"Miami\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami_Hurricanes_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami_Hurricanes_football\"}, {\"begin\": 12962, \"end\": 12968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lando_Norris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.976005406009526e-69, \"text\": \"Norris\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lando_Norris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lando_Norris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was also a difficult weekend for Verstappen, who finished 17th in the sprint -- his first pointless finish in any race format since the 2016 Belgian Grand Prix -- and then fourth in the main race after starting on pole.\", \"from\": 12984, \"to\": 13206, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Horner exit  There were rumblings across the paddock in the first half of the season that all was not well at Red Bull and had not been since the storm in 2024 when a female team employee had accused principal Christian Horner of sexual misconduct.\", \"from\": 13208, \"to\": 13456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13418, \"end\": 13434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_Horner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Christian Horner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_Horner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_Horner\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the beginning of July, Verstappen's car was struggling to keep pace with the McLarens, which led to whispers that Mercedes were lining up a bid to snatch him away.\", \"from\": 13458, \"to\": 13624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13575, \"end\": 13583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mercedes-Benz_in_Formula_One\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.967572349429648e-52, \"text\": \"Mercedes\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mercedes-Benz_in_Formula_One\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mercedes-Benz_in_Formula_One\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Red Bull needed to act and did so by sacking Horner.\", \"from\": 13626, \"to\": 13678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13671, \"end\": 13677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Horner\", \"score\": 0.9999806591200919, \"rank\": 1.934125365903275e-05, \"text\": \"Horner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Horner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Horner\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was not an instant fix, but in his third race under new principal Laurent Mekies, at home in the Netherlands, Verstappen was back on the podium.\", \"from\": 13680, \"to\": 13827, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13749, \"end\": 13763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurent_Mekies\", \"score\": 0.9999983868641998, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laurent Mekies\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurent_Mekies\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurent_Mekies\"}, {\"begin\": 13780, \"end\": 13791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999953461156, \"rank\": 4.653887157563901e-09, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He still trailed championship leader Piastri by 104 points but went on to win the next two races at Monza and Azerbaijan.\", \"from\": 13829, \"to\": 13950, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13929, \"end\": 13934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monza_Circuit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.135242565779966e-49, \"text\": \"Monza\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monza_Circuit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monza_Circuit\"}, {\"begin\": 13939, \"end\": 13949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2019_Azerbaijan_Grand_Prix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.400834229407595e-25, \"text\": \"Azerbaijan\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2019_Azerbaijan_Grand_Prix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2019_Azerbaijan_Grand_Prix\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bump 'n bruise  McLaren kept Verstappen in the reckoning by allowing their two drivers to race each other without team instructions.\", \"from\": 13952, \"to\": 14084, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13968, \"end\": 13975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McLaren\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.387695858836223e-53, \"text\": \"McLaren\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McLaren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McLaren\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That led to some rough and tumble on the track with Norris not finishing in Canada after slamming into Piastri.\", \"from\": 14086, \"to\": 14197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14138, \"end\": 14144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lando_Norris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.976005406009526e-69, \"text\": \"Norris\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lando_Norris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lando_Norris\"}, {\"begin\": 14162, \"end\": 14168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9999996302540923, \"rank\": 3.2391599341213603e-07, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Norris apologized but showed a tougher streak when he barged past Piastri for a podium in Singapore, the race that secured McLaren the constructors' title with six races still left.\", \"from\": 14199, \"to\": 14380, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14199, \"end\": 14205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lando_Norris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.976005406009526e-69, \"text\": \"Norris\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lando_Norris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lando_Norris\"}, {\"begin\": 14289, \"end\": 14298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 0.9956040779214812, \"rank\": 0.004415331532138254, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"