e/Lando_Norris\"}, {\"begin\": 14525, \"end\": 14536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1968_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.23456643057281e-23, \"text\": \"Mexico City\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1968_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1968_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 14541, \"end\": 14550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S\\u00e3o_Paulo\", \"score\": 0.9858779573453796, \"rank\": 0.012363781011925925, \"text\": \"Sao Paulo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S\\u00e3o_Paulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S\\u00e3o_Paulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He could not win the title in Las Vegas, but he could knock Verstappen out of the race.\", \"from\": 14710, \"to\": 14797, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14740, \"end\": 14749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Las_Vegas_Motor_Speedway\", \"score\": 0.9999999331948879, \"rank\": 6.679998870012989e-08, \"text\": \"Las Vegas\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Las_Vegas_Motor_Speedway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Las_Vegas_Motor_Speedway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, it was the Dutchman who came out smiling after overtaking pole-sitter Norris on the first turn and holding the lead all the way to the chequered flag.\", \"from\": 14799, \"to\": 14958, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14819, \"end\": 14827, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9994581892524563, \"rank\": 0.0005421044650287008, \"text\": \"Dutchman\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 14878, \"end\": 14884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lando_Norris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.976005406009526e-69, \"text\": \"Norris\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http:/